WEBVTT

00:00:59.875 --> 00:01:02.059
This would be so devastating

00:01:02.083 --> 00:01:04.643
that no parent would be able to bear it,

00:01:04.667 --> 00:01:05.934
so it's disguised.

00:01:05.958 --> 00:01:09.226
In India, we call this "adjusting."

00:01:09.250 --> 00:01:10.792
I'm sure you've heard the word.

00:01:11.625 --> 00:01:13.684
"Darling, just adjust a bit.

00:01:13.708 --> 00:01:14.976
Just adjust.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:17.976
No matter what happens, just adjust."

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:21.809
"Adjust" trains girls to be powerless,

00:01:21.833 --> 00:01:24.393
not to exist, not to be seen,

00:01:24.417 --> 00:01:26.101
not to have a self,

00:01:26.125 --> 00:01:32.518
and it trains boys to claim power
and authority over the world.